<p>
<h1>Get apps by status</h1> 
</p>

<div class="row">
	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;"><p>
		<b>API Platform Base Path:</b>
		<p>https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}</p>
		<b>API Resource Path:</b>
		<p>/apps?status={status}</p>
		<p>
		Returns all apps with the status of approved, revoked, or pending
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;">
		<p>
		<b>Verb:</b>
		<span class="verb-GET">GET</span>
		</p>
		<b>Auth:</b>
		Basic Auth
		</p>


	</div>
</div>

<div class="span18">
	<p>
	
	</p>

	<b>cURL:</b>
	<pre>curl -u myname:mypass https ://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{myorg}/apps?status=approved</pre>

	<b>Sample Request:</b>
	<pre>$ curl https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}/apps?&quot;status=approved&quot; \
-u myname:mypass</pre>


<b>Sample Response:</b> 
	<pre>[ "app2.1", "app2.2", "MyTestApp", "app3.1", "app1.1", "app3.2", "app1.2", "app4.1" ]</pre>




</div>


            </div>
